imageDescription: The image is a broken piggy bank, shattered into pieces, with money scattered all around. Each piece represents a stolen piece of the singer's heart, symbolizing how the person they loved took everything from them. The shattered piggy bank signifies the singer's realization that they have nothing left to give, and they are no longer willing to be robbed of their love.
